{"tid":871903,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"(hxh)到底富奸係鐘意定好憎信長呢個角色?","createTime":"2018-10-22T10:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T14:03:54.000Z","uid":95520,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"338039120570ba2ce494571e3c69816fc1658949","tid":871903,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:08:33.000Z","msg":"正常我諗旅團原班底所有成員富奸都當佢哋親生仔咁愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但信長呢個角色喺旅團入面嘅定位主要都係柒同搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目前為止仲未見過信長有任何功績<br />\n<br />\n打十陰獸又得佢坐喺中間走唔甩比人活捉左<br />\n團員又撚狗咁撚唔放佢出黎住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後旅團最經理嗰幕屠城滅黑社會,最主要都係拎黎比旅團型<br />\n但信長就留喺屋企看門口睇住兩個細路<br />\n仲要比佢哋走甩埋,最好笑係開圓之後下一秒就影兩個細路走甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n事後仲要比飛坦話就算信長唔喺道都順利搞得掂個任務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n團員自己組團返流星街打蟻又唔預信長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家好不容易喺船上面等到旅團出場<br />\n又比飛坦同迴天串佢唔正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到底富奸係鐘唔鐘意信長呢個角色<br />\n先比個咁嘅位佢做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9275d185b8cd44aa10659217b64e24c86b4a7c","tid":871903,"uid":181527,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"又笑人四米圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f530c8d3c2aa5a6bf313a5daed2f3f80e733f1e8","tid":871903,"uid":129660,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:35:03.000Z","msg":"就係有少少柒先吸引"},{"pid":"cf05dfcdcd25a0e13905c48eb895d5bb50b254e2","tid":871903,"uid":8636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:44:36.000Z","msg":"富奸點諗我就唔知<br />\n淨係知連登又好百度又好<br />\n都好多信長吹<br />\n吹到佢圓唔止咁細，只不過係唔需要咁細<br />\n因為開圓開到佢斬到嘅範圍就無撚敵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1018594aa95cb892c7dbe229533c1c87ffdb80a","tid":871903,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb9275d185b8cd44aa10659217b64e24c86b4a7c","tid":871903,"uid":181527,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"又笑人四米圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:09:43.000Z","msg":"無笑佢四米圓<br />\n係笑佢好型咁開圓嗰一秒就比兩個細路走甩"},{"pid":"f41b1129ba1c8aad94f8f3ab78bb051236d3f619","tid":871903,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf05dfcdcd25a0e13905c48eb895d5bb50b254e2","tid":871903,"uid":8636,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:44:36.000Z","msg":"富奸點諗我就唔知<br />\n淨係知連登又好百度又好<br />\n都好多信長吹<br />\n吹到佢圓唔止咁細，只不過係唔需要咁細<br />\n因為開圓開到佢斬到嘅範圍就無撚敵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"我唔知佢個圓可以有幾大<br />\n但的確唔需要多過4米啊<br />\n你最多揮到4米<br />\n咁比你detect到5米外嘅嘢都無用架"},{"pid":"5619252cceb2685f0023136ff1c650e8c861f40f","tid":871903,"uid":353,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"又要幫信長平反<br />\n佢當然廢過基爺好多<br />\n但佢嘅圓只需要係刀斬到嘅範圍<br />\n斬唔到 個圓開到萬里長城咁都無用<br />\n<br />\n例：基仔個圓仲細<br />\n但係可以完封蝴蝶佬"},{"pid":"8fbd12a534789c0b2457b74a6efbf682f7ce792f","tid":871903,"uid":95520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"我唔係想討論佢個圓啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d19a0b3c71f4bbb86af615c97e445eb2c3ac78f","tid":8719